t, too. \"If I see Connor mcgregor, I'm going to break your weak ass ankle,\" Garcia posted on X Friday afternoon. \"You ran from being tested bc you were on Roids. Roadhouse or ROIDRAGE.\" He later added: \"Bare knuckle. Let’s f-cking go CONNOR. Winner gets your trash ass whiskey brand.\"  This certainly isn't the first time McGregor has been accused of juicing, but the former UFC champ has never tested positive for a banned substance. He's been tested five times already in 2024.",
