 Unleashes Wi&hellip;</span></li></ul></nav></div><h1 class="headline">Conor McGregor Unleashes Wild Rant About Ryan Garcia, Calls For Lifetime Ban After Failed Drug Test</h1><!----><div class="article-meta article-meta-lower"><div class="author-byline"><span class="author-list"><!--[--><span class="author"><a href="https://www.outkick.com/person/h/amber-harding" rel="author">Amber Harding</a></span><!--]--><!----></span><!----></div><div class="article-date"><span class="article-date-published"><strong>Published</strong><time class="time time-published" datetime="May 3, 2024 7:00 PM EDT">May 3, 2024 7:00 PM EDT</time></span><span class="article-date-updated"><span class="dateline-vertical-line">|</span><strong>Updated</strong><time class="time time-updated" datetime="May 3, 2024 7:00 PM EDT">May 3, 2024 7:00 PM EDT</time></span></div><div class="social-icons"><ul><li class="fb"><button>Facebook</button></li><li class="tw"><button>Twitter</button></li><li class="email"><button>Email</button></li><li class="link"><button>Copy Link</button></li></ul></div></div></header><div class="article-body"><div class="featured featured-video video-ct"><div class="video-wrapper"><div class="video-container contextual" id="video-container-1"><script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jwplayer.com/libraries/vAzrGenu.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jwplayer.com/players/5qVYAY5t-ZZoOaN5D.js?search=__CONTEXTUAL__"></script></div></div></div><!--[--><p>Conor McGregor once believed Ryan Garcia <a href="https://www.outkick.com/sports/conor-mcgregor-cheers-up-ryan-garcia-with-inspirational-chat-after-getting-embarrassed-by-gervonta-tank-davis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">was the &quot;future&quot; of boxing</a>. But after reports that Garcia failed his drug test ahead of his fight against Devin Haney, &quot;The Notorious&quot; is singing a different tune.</p><p>In <a href="https://twitter.com/HappyPunch/status/1786247351801155898" target="_blank" rel="noopener">a since-deleted post on Twitter / X</a>, McGregor unleashed a savage tirade against the 25-year-old lightweight &#x2014; even calling for him never to set foot in the ring again.</p><p>&quot;Cheated the weight and was juiced, lifetime ban,&quot; McGregor said. &quot; .... Don&apos;t come near me if I ever see you Ryan Garcia. I am actually disgusted. This ostarine it reminds me of Sean O&apos;Malley was on that as well. I don&apos;t like this, I&apos;ll bust yous both up, do yous want a spar I will set flights right now for you both for a full on spar each.&quot;</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><!--[--><!--[--><!--]--><div class="tweet-embed" loading="lazy"></div><!--]--></div><p>Garcia reportedly tested positive for Ostarine, a substance used to aid performance by helping athletes build muscle mass, enhance their rate of fat loss and increase stamina and recovery ability. O&apos;Malley, a UFC fighter, tested positive for the same performance-enhancing drug in both 2018 and 2019.</p><p>&quot;I&apos;ll ride you both like yous are ostriches,&quot; McGregor continued. &quot;.... If I was Haney&apos;s dad you&apos;re dead no matter what for doing that. Crazy. What the f-ck happened to you, you little fool. Get your head together cos I gonna smash it in with elbows if you don&apos;t. Fair play Devin well done. Your performance has just become even more heroic. Bravo! Get your head together or kill yourself.&quot;</p><div class="ad-container mobile ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="xs sm"><div id="mw-ad-ban1" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><div class="ad-container tablet ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="md"><div id="tw-ad-lb2" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><div class="ad-container desktop ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="lg xl xxl"><div id="desk-ad-lb2" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><p>Sheesh.</p><h2>Ryan Garcia Fires Back At Conor McGregor</h2><p>Not only does Garcia deny that he ever used PEDs, but he also made the claim that his support of Donald Trump had something to do with the positive test.</p><p>&quot;It&#x2019;s funny I bring up all these things&#x2026;how about Gaza? Protect Trump. All these things that I shouldn&#x2019;t be saying, of course, they&#x2019;re out to get me,&quot; Garcia <a href="https://twitter.com/MichaelBensonn/status/1785935678578065655" target="_blank" rel="noopener">said in an Instagram Live video</a>.</p><p><strong>READ:</strong> <a href="https://www.outkick.com/sports/ryan-garcia-positive-ped-test-donald-trump-support" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ryan Garcia Shares Theory That His Positive PED Test Is A Result Of Being A Donald Trump Supporter</strong></a></p><div class="embed-media twitter"><!--[--><!--[--><!--]--><div class="tweet-embed" loading="lazy"></div><!--]--></div><p>Garcia had something to say about McGregor&apos;s rant, too.</p><div class="ad-container mobile ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="xs sm"><div id="mw-ad-ban2" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><div class="ad-container tablet ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="md"><div id="tw-ad-lb3" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><div class="ad-container desktop ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="lg xl xxl"><div id="desk-ad-lb3" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><p>&quot;If I see Connor mcgregor, I&apos;m going to break your weak ass ankle,&quot; Garcia <a href="https://twitter.com/RyanGarcia/status/1786462011968369115" target="_blank" rel="noopener">posted on X Friday</a> afternoon. &quot;You ran from being tested bc you were on Roids. Roadhouse or ROIDRAGE.&quot;</p><p><a href="https://x.com/RyanGarcia/status/1786480243076702392" target="_blank" rel="noopener">He later added</a>: &quot;Bare knuckle. Let&#x2019;s f-cking go CONNOR. Winner gets your trash ass whiskey brand.&quot;</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><!--[--><!--[--><!--]--><div class="tweet-embed" loading="lazy"></div><!--]--></div><p>This certainly isn&apos;t the first time McGregor has been accused of juicing, but the former UFC champ has never tested positive for a banned substance. He&apos;s been tested <a href="https://www.mensjournal.com/news/conor-mcgregor-ufc-doping-test" target="_blank" rel="noopener">five times already</a> in 2024.</p><!--]--></div><footer class="article-footer"><div class="article-tags tags"><div class="title">Tags</div><ul><!--[--><li><a href="https://www.outkick.com/category/ryan-garcia">#Ryan Garcia</a></li><li><a href="https://www.outkick.com/category/conor-mcgregor">#Conor McGregor</a></li><li><a href="https://www.outkick.com/category/boxing">#Boxing</a></li><!--]--></ul></div><!--[--><div class="author-bio author-1"><!----><div class="info"><div class="author-name"><span>Written by <a href="https://www.outkick.com/person/h/amber-harding" rel="author">Amber Harding</a></span></div><span class="author-dek">Amber is a Midwestern transplant living in Murfreesboro, TN. She spends most of her time taking pictures of her dog, explaining why real-life situations are exactly like "this one time on South Park," and being disappointed by the Tennessee Volunteers.</span><div class="social-icons"><ul><!--[--><li class="ig"><a href="https://http://instagram.com/amberharding">instagram</a></li><li class="tw"><a href="https://https://twitter.com/theamberharding">twitter</a></li><li class="email"><a href="https://mailto:amber.harding@outkick.com">email</a></li><!--]--></ul></div></div></div><!--]--></footer><div class="vendor-units"><div data-uid="AR_1" class="vendor-unit" data-vendor="outbrain"></div><div data-uid="MB_1" class="vendor-unit" data-vendor="outbrain"></div></div></div><aside class="sidebar sidebar-1"><!--[--><!--[--><div class="ad-container desktop ad-w-300 ad-h-250" data-size="lg xl xxl"><div id="desk-ad-ban1" class="ad"></div><!----><span></span></div><div class="item item-newsletter"><h2 class="title">Get the Daily OutKick and get smarter every day.</h2><div class="content"><div class="_form_44"></div><script src="https://outkick.activeho